1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,840
[EP. 05] Before I Noticed You

2
00:00:11,740 --> 00:00:12,840
Why soup?

3
00:00:12,840 --> 00:00:14,740
You kept saying how hot it was…

4
00:00:15,700 --> 00:00:16,700
I don’t know..

5
00:00:16,700 --> 00:00:17,380
So hot..

6
00:00:17,380 --> 00:00:18,420
Did you drink last night?

7
00:00:18,420 --> 00:00:19,040
Speak for yourself.

8
00:00:22,460 --> 00:00:23,700
Geez…What are you doing!?

9
00:00:27,360 --> 00:00:27,860
Oh,

10
00:00:28,340 --> 00:00:29,380
Hello, Ha Eun

11
00:00:29,380 --> 00:00:30,840
Hey, Wook

12
00:00:30,840 --> 00:00:32,150
You’re here to eat alone?

13
00:00:32,150 --> 00:00:33,160
Where’s Yeo Reum?

14
00:00:33,160 --> 00:00:34,280
Yeo Reum?

15
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:36,200
She’s coming after her team project meeting.

16
00:00:41,840 --> 00:00:43,780
He would just not say hi, huh?

17
00:00:44,160 --> 00:00:45,340
Definitely not my type.

18
00:00:45,640 --> 00:00:49,180
Hey, say something. Ha Eun is here.

19
00:00:49,180 --> 00:00:50,740
Ha Eun, have you seen him talk?

20
00:00:51,160 --> 00:00:52,080
Not really…

21
00:00:52,500 --> 00:00:55,080
He really likes cute things.

22
00:00:55,820 --> 00:00:56,920
Whenever he sees cats, he just…

23
00:00:56,920 --> 00:00:57,420
Argh

24
00:00:59,540 --> 00:01:00,400
What? Cats?

25
00:01:00,820 --> 00:01:02,300
Oh… It’s nothing…

26
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:04,140
Make an order…

27
00:01:04,140 --> 00:01:04,940
But you, seriously…

28
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:08,950
Is Yeo Reum coming late?

29
00:01:08,950 --> 00:01:10,940
No, she said she’d be here soon.

30
00:01:11,780 --> 00:01:13,600
Isn’t it hot today?

31
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:14,940
I should order something cool.

32
00:01:17,740 --> 00:01:18,240
Ah?

33
00:01:22,500 --> 00:01:24,360
What are you doing? You said you were hot.

34
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:27,700
I’m cold now.

35
00:01:34,580 --> 00:01:35,460
What’s up with him…

36
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:40,460
Consideration; the first step to noticing others

37
00:01:40,660 --> 00:01:42,440
Hi hi, sorry I’m late.

38
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:44,160
You must be hungry. Order something.

39
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:47,280
I’m hot after running here.

40
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:48,840
I should get something cold.

41
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:57,960
A Day Before Us

